    Product description

    Mintra Boots "CAIWIRE" is your best choice.The best combination of comfort and style with lace-up shoes to tighten and expand at will. The upper of "CAIWire" is made with high precision technology. The upper fabric allows for superior breathability of the legs and the lace up to adjust the shoe to your liking. The sole is specially made from EVA making it the lightest and most comfortable ever. 18 different colors

    This footwear collection is uniquely designed as a laced slip-on shoe, accompanied by a pull tab to put the shoes on & off as quickly as possible, which will work great for those busy bees.
